@NODE fonctions "Overview"



	      *   Compress and Decompress with DMS
	      *   Locale support
	      *   Take the name of the volume for name of file
		  (eg ; floppy name : pagestream3
		  give  file name   : pagestream3.dms)
	      *   Automatique Recognition of floppy format (HD PC) as well as
		  read than write
	      


@ENDNODE
@NODE Config "Required Configuration"




	      * @{"MUI 3.X" LINK mui}
	      * SYSTEM 2.04  or more
	      * @{"DMS" LINK dms}

@ENDNODE

