@NODE SAUVER "Save Default settings"




		 Save the actual settings as default


@ENDNODE
@NODE SAUVERCOMME "Save settings as ..."




		 Save the actual settings with a name.
		 e.g. archives, games, foobar, etc ...

@ENDNODE

@NODE CHARGER "Load default Settings"



		 Load default settings, if you were loaded others settings.
		


@ENDNODE
@NODE CHARGERCOMME "Load Settings as ..."





		 Load settings saved with a name.
		 e.g. archives, games, foobar, etc ...

@ENDNODE


